description: The story is about a dad telling his children about the threat of communism. He had almost fallen for the lies himself, but his sincere belief in God led him straight again and got the communist that tried to turn him arrested by the F.B.I. This comic, from the cold war era, was part of the Christian Anti-Communist Crusade propaganda.
This magazine with car cover and glossy pages came in beautiful psychedelic colors.
